2026-05-13T16:25:55.3143816Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T16:25:55.3144939Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T16:25:55.3145798Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T16:25:55.3146841Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-13T16:25:55.3147667Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-13T16:25:55.3148464Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
